</div>
<br />
<div class="blockquote">
<p><strong>日期：</strong>██/05/13</p>
<p><strong>事件经过：</strong>Misaka19092nd于其他站点工作时在该站点附近种植大量番茄，导致Blast博士错以为SCP-504收容失效。</p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:95%;"><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/10/22/xbZjBC1UasIXei8.png" style="width:95%;" alt="xbZjBC1UasIXei8.png" class="image" />
