<p><strong>十月二十四日晚</strong></p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:96%;"><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/10/24/wEpscSalxeYivRN.jpg" style="width:96%;" alt="wEpscSalxeYivRN.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:96%;">
<p>Misaka亲手烤的巧克力曲奇</p>
</div>
</div>
<p>这个分页终于有用了！</p>
</div>
<div id="wiki-tab-0-5" style="display:none">
<p>有人能留点言么……</p>
<div class="blockquote">
<p>就在这里用&gt;代码留言吧，记得加上用户名！</p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p>恭喜提人事ヾ ^_^♪，这娃……还是收容了吧……<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/confucian-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6591621); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6591621&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610194948" alt="Confucian Lee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6591621)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/confucian-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6591621); return false;">Confucian Lee</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>（剧组可以考虑把超炮改编成音乐剧了 ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zzzzzac" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5215451); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5215451&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610194948" alt="ZZZZZac" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5215451)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zzzzzac" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5215451); return false;">ZZZZZac</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>“我弄成了”</p>
<p>“来留点言吧（”</p>
